name: Array(el1,el2,el3)
description: Add values to an Array variable.

name: AscB(String)
description: Return the byte code for a character.

name: .BrowseForFolder
description: Prompt the user to select a folder.

name: Chr(ChrCode)
description: Return the string character for ChrCode (ASCII code)

name: ChrB(ChrCode)
description: Return the string character for ChrCode (Byte code)

name: ChrW(ChrCode)
description: Return the string character for ChrCode (Unicode/DBCS)

name: .CreateObject
description: Create an automation object / run an external command.

name: .CurrentDirectory
description: Retrieve or change the current directory.

name: DateAdd
description: Add a time interval to a Date.

name: DateDiff
description: Return the time interval between two dates.

name: DatePart
description: Return part of a given date.

name: DateSerial
description: Return a Date from a numeric Year, Month and Day.

name: DateValue
description: Return a Date from a string expression.

name: Day(date)
description: Return the day component of date (1-31)

name: Dim
description: Declare a new variable or array variable.

name: .Echo
description: Echo text to screen, also StdOut.Write /.Popup

name: Escape(String)
description: Return only ASCII characters from a Unicode string.

name: Exp(n)
description: Return e (base of natural logs) raised to a power n.

name: Exit
description: Exit a block of code immediately.

name: FileSystemObject
description: Work with Drives, Folders and Files.

name: Filter
description: Produce an array by filtering an existing array.

name: Fix(number)
description: Return the integer portion of a number.

name: For...Next
description: Repeat a block of statements a given number of times.

name: For Each...
description: Loop through the items in a collection or array.

name: FormatCurrency
description: Format a number with a currency symbol.

name: FormatPercent
description: Format a number with a % symbol.

name: Hex(number)
description: Return the hex value of number.

name: Hour(time)
description: h     Return the hour component of time.

name: If..Then
description: Conditionally execute a block of statements.

name: InStrRev
description: Find one string within another, starting from the end.

name: Int(number)
description: Return the integer portion of a number.

name: Join
description: Combine the contents of an array into a single variable.

name: LBound
description: Return the smallest subscript for an array.

name: Left(String,len)
description: Return the leftmost len characters of string.

name: Len(String)
description: Return length of string in characters.

name: .LogEvent
description: Log an item in the Event log.

name: LTrim(String)
description: Remove any leading spaces from a string expression.

name: Mid
description: Return a mid-section from a string.

name: Minute(time)
description: Return the minute component of time.

name: Month(date)
description: Return the month component of date.

name: MonthName
description: Convert a month number to a descriptive Month.

name: Now
description: Return the current Date and Time.

name: Option Explicit
description: Force all variables to be defined

name: Right(String,len)
description: Return the rightmost len characters of string.

name: Round
description: Round a number to n decimal places.

name: RTrim(String)
description: Remove any trailing spaces from a string expression.

name: Second(time)
description: Return the second component of time.

name: Select...Case
description: Conditionally execute a block of statements.

name: .ShellExecute
description: Run a script/application in the Windows Shell.

name: Space
description: Return a string consisting of spaces.

name: Split
description: Parse a string of delimited values into an array.

name: StdOut.Read
description: Obtain User Input from the command prompt.

name: StdOut.Write
description: Echo text to the screen, also beep.

name: String
description: Create a string with a single character repeated.

name: TimeSerial
description: Construct a Time value from Hours, Minutes and seconds

name: TimeValue
description: Convert a string to a Time value.

name: Trim(String)
description: Remove leading and trailing spaces from string

name: UBound
description: Return the largest subscript for an array dimension

name: UnEscape(Str)
description: Return Unicode characters from an escaped ASCII string

name: Weekday
description: Return the day of the week (1-7)

name: WeekdayName
description: Return the named day of the week

name: While...Wend
description: Conditionally repeat a block of statements

name: With
description: Assign multiple properties of an object

name: Year(date)
description: Return the year component of date (1-12)
